.:: Zebra puzzle ::.
There are 5 different favourite colors: red, green, ivory, yellow, blue
There 5 different types of food: papaya, onion, asparagus, pineapple, kiwi
House: colonial, cape-cod, victorian, modern, gothic-revival
There are 5 different favourite beverages: coffee, tea, milk, orange-juice, water
5 different pets are kept: dog, fox, zebra, horse, snails

1. the person eating papaya is the person who likes red
2. the person eating onion is the owner of the dog
3. the person drinking coffee is the person who likes green
4. the person eating asparagus is the person drinking tea
5. the person who likes green is to the right of the person who likes ivory
6. the colonial house is the owner of the snails
7. the cape-cod house is the person who likes yellow
8. the person drinking milk is in the middle
9. the person eating pineapple is on the far left
10. the victorian house is on the left or right of the owner of the fox
11. the cape-cod house is to the left or right of the owner of the horse
12. the modern house is the person drinking orange-juice
13. the person eating kiwi is the gothic-revival house
14. the person eating pineapple is to the left or right of the person who likes blue

.:: Answer ::.
|		|       1	|	2	|	3 	|	4	|	5	|
| Food	|   pineapple	|    asparagus	|     papaya	|    onion	|    kiwi	|
| Color		|    yellow	|      blue	|      red	|     ivory	|     green	|
| Beverage	|     water	|      tea	|      milk	| orange-juice	|     coffee	|
| House		|     cape-cod	| chesterfield	|    olg-gold	| modern	|   parliament	|
| Pet		|     fox	|     horse	|     snails	|     dog	|     zebra	|
